    "description": "Grow your career with McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd! We are hiring a Reservation Manager for our Jaipur team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nMcDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
